race.comment: STOICISM (5) arrives in winning form after a determined neck victory over this track and trip, continuing her consistent run of late. She looks well placed to repeat the dose and remains a leading contender. GREY NORTHERN (9) bounced back to winning form at Toowoomba last start and deserves respect. MAD ANA (7) should be ready to peak after two runs back, the latest effort a fourth over 1800m at this track. Include everywhere. DEEP DRIVE (6) finished midfield last start at Gold Coast Poly over 1540m, 2 lengths from the winner. Tackles a longer journey this time and can give this a shake. STEEL IMPACT (10) is always thereabouts and worth including in wider plays.
